{"tid":2122951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃絲媽勁過黃絲仔","createTime":"2020-07-24T09:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T10:52:44.000Z","uid":36861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f909fe040d1e8f5143ee4d23199472e9da5ad03b","tid":2122951,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:54:10.000Z","msg":"嗰個就係我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是咁的，話說我都受過小小所謂高等教育，昨日在某網同d回流所謂高等五毛藍絲展開網上罵戰，小弟不才，在以寡敵眾之下，屢敗屢戰。唯五毛如樓蟻眾多，敵盈我疲，終敗走。<br />\n<br />\n今日返老母屋企食飯，佢話聽到啲同事喺度講咩大陸點好點好，之後佢發現嗰個女人同事原來係喺大陸返嚟嘅，仲要呃綜援。之後我老母聽到火滾，大大聲屌咗句：「中国咁把炮你咪返去你嘅中国囉，使乜喺度呃綜援呀？」所有同事靜晒。<br />\n<br />\n個阿姐敗走。<br />\n<br />\n個故事教訓讀書多未必有用，最緊要係有氣勢。<br />\n<br />\n 阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以後會準時交家用㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e91ed2a068c254004c36a785f64f848d34f3f63","tid":2122951,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁老母"},{"pid":"44e9a145361d34086715bb4fa814eb45539bc75c","tid":2122951,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"鍾意伯母"}]}